  <zone type="main">
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_0">illustrates them, must be the same.—</line>
    
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_1"><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0077.03"/><hi rend="underline">Ion</hi><anchor
        xml:id="e1-0077.03"/> As<hi rend="underline">sur</hi>edly <milestone unit="tei:speaker"
        spanTo="#e1-0077.x"/><hi rend="underline">Soc</hi>.<anchor xml:id="e1-0077.x"/> Yet <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">if</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear reason="illegible">progress</unclear></del>
        <del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear">in the</add></del>
        </mod> </line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_2"><del rend="strikethrough">consider<add>ation</add></del><mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear"><unclear reason="illegible">of</unclear></add>
      </mod> any other art<mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">;</del>
        <add place="intralinear">—</add>
      </mod> <add place="superlinear"><del><unclear reason="illegible">of</unclear> speak</del> of</add> the same</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_3">mode of consideration must be</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_4"><unclear reason="illegible">admitted</unclear> with respect to all arts; do</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_5">you desire to hear what I understand</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_6">by this, o Ion? <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0077.04"/><hi rend="underline"
        >Ion</hi>.<anchor xml:id="e1-0077.04"/>— Yes, by Jupiter</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_7">o Socrates. I am delighted with listening</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_8">to you <del rend="strikethrough">philosophers</del><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">.</del>
        <add place="superlinear"><unclear reason="case">W</unclear>ise  </add>
      </mod>
      <unclear reason="case">M</unclear>en. Soc.</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_9">To confess the truth, it is you who</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_10">ar<mod>
        <del rend="smear">t</del>
        <add place="intralinear">e</add>
      </mod> wise, o Ion. The raphsodists,</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_11">the actors, &amp; the authors</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_12"><del rend="strikethrough">Children of Hell</del></line>
    <line  xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_13" rend="indent2"><del rend="strikethrough">Herald of Gods darest thou delay</del>
      <del rend="unmarked">...</del></line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_14">Darest thou delay o Herald! <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten"><unclear reason="illegible">c</unclear></del>
        <add place="intralinear">t</add>
      </mod>ake cheer <unclear reason="case">H</unclear>ounds</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0077.02"/>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_15">Of Hell — what if the Son of Maia soon</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_16" rend="indent1">Sh<hi rend="sup">d</hi>. make</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0077.02"/>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_17">Of <unclear reason="illegible">those</unclear> poems which you recite. <del
        rend="strikethrough"><unclear>&amp;</unclear></del></line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_18">I, like an unprofessional &amp; private</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-ion_line_19">man, can only say that which I</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-pu_line_0"><add><metamark function="unclear" rend="short_vertical_line"/></add>The contrast would have been completeter if the
      sentiment</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-pu_line_1">had been transposed: but wherefore sacrifize the philoso</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-pu_line_2">phical truth, that love however monstrous in its expression</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-pu_line_3">is still less worthy of <unclear reason="illegible">horror</unclear> than hatred <unclear
      reason="illegible">—</unclear>
      <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear reason="illegible">the</unclear></del> perhaps in</line>
    <line xml:id="e1-0077-pu_line_4"><unclear reason="illegible">whatever degree</unclear></line>
